==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Comprehensor
<hw>Com`pre*hen"sor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
comprehends; one who has attained to a full knowledge.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>When I shall have dispatched this weary pilgrimage, and from a
traveler shall come to be a <qex>comprehensor</qex>, farewell faith and
welcome vision.</q> <rj><qau>Bp. Hall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Compress</ent>⟦br⟧
